            <title>[LU-1630] Test failure on test suite sanity-scrub, subtest test_9</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1630</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for sarah &amp;lt;sarah@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/5e87ca5e-cd0e-11e1-9a56-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/5e87ca5e-cd0e-11e1-9a56-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_9 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;(12) Unexpected speed 275, should not more than 270&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: sanity-scrub 9&lt;/p&gt;</description>
